<p style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">Thank you for voting us as Best of Solano!</p>
<p>Here at Vallejo Floor Company, we realize that the slowing economy has had negative effects on just about everybody.  Because of this people have been forced to choose between quality and price when shopping for their flooring and cabinetry needs.  This is not a decision we at Vallejo Floor Company feel anyone should ever have to make.  Because of this, we are working more than ever in order to get the absolute best pricing possible for all of our customers.  Stop in or call today, and one of our friendly, knowledgeable staff members will assist you and ensure that you'll get the best price possible.</p>